Dear Colleague:

Need information on retail energy markets?

Retail Energy Foresight, a bimonthly publication with switch
rate predictions and thoughtful analysis, is what you need
to understand today's volatile retail energy markets.

Download FREE trial issues from XENERGY's web site at
http://www.xenergy.com/foresight

Every issue of Retail Energy Foresight presents:

 --> Switch rates by utility service territory and customer
class from around the nation;

--> Predictions of switch rates for Pennsylvania, Illinois,
and other markets;

--> An intimate look at markets and related topics; in the
August/September issue, read about Market Backwaters and
potential for revival;

--> All of the above served up with our own brand of humor
to make retail energy markets actually fun to read about.

Take a look at what Retail Energy Foresight has to offer.
We think you'll agree it's a valuable and unique analysis
publication, and hope that you're tempted to subscribe.  To
do so, print out and fax back the order form on the last
page of any issue (from our Web site) or call me at
781.273.5700 x387.

Regards,

Susan Weber
Editor - Retail Energy Foresight
