holiday costumes.  Possible outfits include but are not limited to:

Santa, Chanukah Monkey, Reindeer, Winter Warlock, Elf, Rabbi, Jesus,
Kwanzameister Meister Kwanza, Hermy, Dradle, Christmas Tree, Tooth Fairy
